title: Ep - 93 - KELLEY WOLF FROM REAL WORLD / LOGAN NOH FROM VANDERPUMP RULES
description:
Kelley Wolf from Real World: New Orleans and Road Rules talks about her experience on reality television, gives her unique perspective on how fame impacts the brain, and catches us up on life in Utah where she lives with her husband actor Scott Wolf and their three kids. 


Logan Noh from Vanderpump Rules explains his relationship with James Kennedy. Logan is a photographer and an art director for commercials and music videos. His clients include Bruno Mars and Erika Jayne. He also gives his insight into this season of Real Housewives of Beverly Hills. 


Troy Turner from Taste of Reality reviews Gold Rush on the Discovery Channel.


Kate’s older sister Megan reviews the season finale of The Bachelor.
